ZH: 蓝领工人通常是从事体力劳动的人。
EN: Blue-collar workers are usually people who do physical labor.

ZH: 这个城市的蓝领工作机会很多。
EN: There are many blue-collar job opportunities in this city.

ZH: 蓝领工作可能比较辛苦，但是也很重要。
EN: Blue-collar jobs may be tough, but they are also very important.

ZH: 许多蓝领工人每天都在建筑工地工作。
EN: Many blue-collar workers work on construction sites every day.

ZH: 蓝领工人往往没有太多的文化知识。
EN: Blue-collar workers often do not have much education.

ZH: 我们应该尊重所有蓝领工人的努力。
EN: We should respect the efforts of all blue-collar workers.

ZH: 蓝领工人在这个社会中扮演着重要的角色。
EN: Blue-collar workers play an important role in this society.

ZH: 很多蓝领工作需要强壮的体魄。
EN: Many blue-collar jobs require a strong physique.

ZH: 我们的经济离不开蓝领工人的辛勤付出。
EN: Our economy depends on the hard work of blue-collar workers.

ZH: 蓝领工人的工作往往没有很多晋升机会。
EN: Blue-collar workers often do not have many opportunities for advancement.

ZH: 蓝领工作可能对身体有影响。
EN: Blue-collar jobs may have an impact on the body.

ZH: 蓝领工人经常需要穿工作服。
EN: Blue-collar workers often need to wear work uniforms.

ZH: 他们家庭的主要经济来源是蓝领工作。
EN: The main source of income for their family is blue-collar work.

ZH: 蓝领工作有时会被低估。
EN: Blue-collar work is sometimes underestimated.

ZH: 很多蓝领工人在工作中放弃了自己的梦想。
EN: Many blue-collar workers give up their dreams in their work.

