EN: Blue-collar workers need to deal with machines regularly.

ZH: 蓝领行业的发展对于整个社会都很重要。
EN: The development of the blue-collar industry is important for the entire society.

ZH: 有些蓝领工人在工作中面临危险。
EN: Some blue-collar workers face danger in their work.

ZH: 蓝领工作可能不是每个人都能胜任的。
EN: Blue-collar jobs may not be suitable for everyone.

ZH: 蓝领工作是社会经济中不可或缺的部分。
EN: Blue-collar work is an indispensable part of the social economy.
